@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Air Transport Company Collaborator" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC

ATCC -> System : Requests to list company fleet by capacity

activate System
System --> ATCC : Requests company and capacity criteria
deactivate System

ATCC -> System : Provides company identification and capacity criteria

activate System
System --> System : Check if collaborator is authorized
System --> System : Validate air transport company
System --> System : Check if collaborator belongs to company
System --> System : Validate capacity criteria
System --> System : Retrieve company fleet
System --> System : Calculate total capacity for each aircraft
System --> System : Filter and/or order aircraft by capacity

alt matching aircraft exist
    System --> ATCC : Display fleet by capacity
else no matching aircraft exist
    System --> ATCC : Display empty list message
else user is not authorized or criteria are invalid
    System --> ATCC : Display error message
end

deactivate System
deactivate ATCC

@enduml